Class ClusOutput

java.lang.Object
si.ijs.kt.clus.main.ClusOutput
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClusErrorOutput
public class ClusOutput extends Object
Class for outputting the training and testing results to .out file. All the information during the process is gathered here.
